<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>MicroMart Activation Email</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #222222;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        a {
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        table td{
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #0070f3;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #fafafa;
        }
        .email-body{
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 24px;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Welcome to MicroMart!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for registering with MicroMart! To complete your registration, please use the following activation code.</p>
            <p>
                <h2><%= otp %></h2>
            </p>
            <p>Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5 minutes.</p>
            <p>If you did not register for MicroMart, please ignore this email.</p>
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>The MicroMart Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at:
                <a href="mailto:akshayjyothip@gmail.com">akshayjyothip@gmail.com</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
